description.Name: description
description.Value:
Redwood Empire Sheep Dog Association
Slaven herding trial, Zamora CA

Wyn ran out to work her sheep, but another dog came from the set up area and chased Wyn's sheep away.  Two of the three went to the gathering area, but it turned out that the third was still in the field over the hill.  Turns out to be a problem...see part 2 :-)
